        ": سمعت الرضا عليه السلام يقول: ما بعث الله نبيا قط إلا بتحريم الخمر وأن يقر لله بالبداء"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "7. [7/365] al-Kafi: Ali b. Ibrahim from his father from al-Rayyan b. al-Salt who said: I heard al-Ridha عليه السلام: Allah has never appointed a prophet except with the prohibition of wine and that he (the prophet) accept from Allah the Bada’"
        ]
